ing: 1 (1.25 ounce) package McCormickÂ® Taco Seasoning Mix
des: "Two cups Greek yogurt and a packet of Taco Mix--it's that easy. Your guests will be wondering what you did! Dip in chips, pretzels, or veggies like cucumbers, peppers or carrots."
ins: Mix 2 cups plain Greek yogurt with 1 package McCormick(R) Taco Seasoning Mix until well blended. Refrigerate until cool, serve and enjoy.
